title: WayFM 2009-03-19 DJ Mixcontest 2009 (Harold Zwaartman 20h-23h)
description:
The goal:

Make a mix which contains at least one track from the 70's, 80's, 90's and 00's within a 7 minutes playtime.


The jury:

Lex van Coevorden
JPL
Jerry Beke
Emile Noordhoek



The DJ mix contest 2009 was organized and broadcasted by Harold Zwaartman of WayFM.  This is a stream rip encoded as a 32KHz lame VBR MP3 with the news bulletines and commercials cut out.

During the broadcast, which features 16 mixes from different DJ's, each entry was judged live by a team of 4 professional/semi-professional producers.  Listeners of the show could add their vote by email, counting as a 5th member of the team.  The names of the DJ's were kept secret until the end of the show.

As WayFM is a Dutch radio station all comments are in Dutch.
